description:
Michael Stephens' Bending Reality TV - http://BendingRealityTV.com

In this interview Michael Stephens catches up with legendary musician George Benson. You may know George by some his songs such as In Your Eyes, Love X Love, Lady Love Me, Greatest Love of All, Love Ballad, Inside Love, On Broadway, This Masquerade, Turn Your Love Around, Give Me The Night. George discusses his charity performance, traveling, Andrea Bocelli, Robin Thicke, his Nat King Cole project and more.
